Backend failure on connect
If connect_backend() fails, mark that backend unhealthy and try the next one.
Retry another backend
Don’t close the client immediately if one backend fails.
Periodic health checks
Every few seconds, attempt to connect to unhealthy backends and mark them healthy if they respond.
Metrics
Print or expose:
active_sessions
registered_backends
healthy_backends
total_connections
backend_failures
bytes_proxied
Config file
Support both:
./lb backends.conf

and dynamic registration.